summary: An ordinance relating to the Public Health Dept.; amending Seattle Municipal Code Chapter 10.13 relating to meat, rabbit, poultry and aquatic foods, consolidating the scopes of licenses of MPRAF wrapper and MPRAF salesperson and simplifying the examination therefor; amending Seattle Municipal Code Subsections 10.13.100, 10.13.120.A, 10.13.120.F, 10.13.150.B, 10.13.160.G, 10.13.400, 10.13.410, 10.03.013.A, 10.03.013.D; and repealing 10.13.160.F.
